    "Providing suggestions, giving recommendations and similar demands all fall under brainstorming.",
    "• Closed QA.",
    "Select the correct option based on the provided prompts and questions or obtain the answer directly or indirectly from the provided textual information.",
    "For Open QA instructions, questions do not come with options, and answers cannot be directly found within the question.",
    "One must rely on their own knowledge base to formulate a response."
